OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud in
OL,6,Fthe east will clear quickly after the
OL,7,Fsunrise. Another bright and sunny day
OL,8,Fis then expected with temperatures
OL,9,Fslightly higher than on Thursday.
OL,10,FGenerally less windy, helping the
OL,11,Fwarmer feel of the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry night will follow with
OL,14,Fclear spells and light winds. Low
OL,15,Fcloud and patchy fog will affect
OL,16,Feastern areas once again towards
OL,17,Fmorning. A chilly night with rural
OL,18,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
