OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLow cloud and fog patches in
OL,6,Fthe east will again clear by mid-
OL,7,Fmorning. A dry day with sunny spells
OL,8,Fthen follows, although cloudier in the
OL,9,Fnortheast. Feeling warm for most.
